Title: Carrot or Stick
Plot: House and the team try to link symptoms of a teenage military recruit and his drill sergeant; House secretly helps Cuddy's daughter get into a prestigious preschool; someone posted a disparaging photo of Chase on a social-networking site.
GuestStars: Patrick Rafferty, Melanie Cruz, Turner Dixon, Elizabeth Ann, Grace Rowe, Nigel Gibbs, Sasha Roiz, Tyler James, Kyle Fain MacDonald, Rachel Melvin, Stella Maeve, Kayla Ewell, Maite Schwartz
